Label 1 Text: Translate from English to BSL
Baby blue screen
Arial font 20 px
Two buttons below
Button1:  ‘Click to speak’
Button 2: ‘Click to type’ 
Empty label beneath

When Button1 clicked:
	Clear label section
Call voice recognition
	Before getting text set label to ’loading...’
After getting results call ‘Break into words’
Check if word is in list of 20 bad words
	()
	If in list remove word from result
Call ‘classify
Classify word in list of time frame, topic or action/comment
	If in time frame list
		Find the match 
			Add to FINAL variable time frame
		If no match
			Place a blank slate 
	elif in topic list
		Find the match 
			Add to FINAL variable topic
		If no match
			Place a blank slate 
	elif in action/comment list
		Find the match 
			Add to FINAL variable action/comment
		If no match
			Place a blank slate 
	Else
		Place a blank slate 
If more than 1 variable per classifications, use hierarchy 

Give symbols of words in order: time frame, topic and action/comment in label2
Return all to same

Click button to type 
	Clear label section
	Before getting text set label to ’loading...
	After getting results call ‘Break into words’
Check if word is in list of 20 bad words
	()
	If in list remove word from result
Call ‘classify
Classify word in list of time frame, topic or action/comment
	If in time frame list
		Find the match 
			Add to variable time frame
		If no match
			Place a blank slate 
	elif in topic list
		Find the match 
			Add to variable topic
		If no match
			Place a blank slate 
	elif in action/comment list
		Find the match 
			Add to variable action/comment
		If no match
			Place a blank slate 
	Else
		Place a blank slate 
If more than 1 variable per classifications, use hierarchy 
Give symbols of words in order: time frame, topic and action/comment in label2
	Return all to same
